  "story": "An exuberant praise hymn that has been a staple of joyful worship in Karnataka churches. The universal cry of 'Hallelujah' is woven with Kannada poetry to create an uplifting congregational song that transcends denominational boundaries. Sung with clapping and great energy in both traditional and charismatic Kannada-speaking congregations.",
